xvi (2.49-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bug fix release
    - "Join" commands now join the right number of line and
      insert and display the right number of spaces
    - Parse exuberant ctags' extended format for tags file
    - Allow saving to a writable file in an unwritable directory
    - Repaint the window when a X Window System terminal window is resized
    - Fixed one potential infinite loop, one seg fault nd one buffer overflow bugs
    - Allow compilation with TinyC (tcc) and without -ansi
    - Get cursor position right after unsuccessful "n" command

 -- Martin Guy <martinwguy@gmail.com>  Thu, 29 Mar 2015 18:26:16 +0200

